      "releaseNotes": "• Improves localization and fixes some minor issues in PaintX\n\nIn upcoming releases we will continue adding new features, and will continue to enhance every aspect of LumaFusion. Find tutorials, reference guide, answers to your questions, and contact us directly at lumatouch.co/support",
